All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
BasePage
BasePage is a utility class that encapsulates common WebDriver operations to interact with web pages.
BlackBoxTestCase
BlackBoxTestCase contains methods for performing black box testing on web applications using Selenium WebDriver.
BusinessRequirementTestCase
BusinessRequirementTestCase contains methods for validating business requirements through database testing.
DatabaseReader
DatabaseReader provides functionalities to interact with a SQL database.
DynamicThreadManager
Manages the execution of tasks in a thread pool with a limited number of permits to control the concurrency.
PerformanceTestCase
PerformanceTestCase contains methods for validating the execution time of test cases, ensuring they meet specified performance criteria.
ProjectTestMain
ProjectTestMain is the main class for executing various test cases for a web application.
ReportManager
ReportManager is responsible for generating and managing test execution reports.
StockPrice
StockPrice is a class designed to interact with web pages for the purpose of fetching stock price information.
SystemInfoUtil
SystemInfoUtil provides static methods to retrieve system performance metrics such as CPU load and memory utilization using the OSHI (Operating System and Hardware Information) library.
TestCaseExecutor
TestCaseExecutor is a utility class for dynamically executing test methods using Java Reflection.
TestMethods
TestMethods contains specific test methods to be executed as part of the testing process.
TestRunner
TestRunner is a class designed to execute a suite of test cases.
WebDriverManager
WebDriverManager is a utility class that encapsulates the management of WebDriver instances.
WhiteBoxTestCase
WhiteBoxTestCase provides methods for white box testing, particularly focusing on testing the functionalities of the database interaction.
